<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Trickster • The final Perl web framework</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0d1117;
            --card: #161b22;
            --border: #30363d;
            --text: #c9d1d9;
            --accent: #ffa657;
            --red: #f0575b;
            --green: #3fb950;
            --link: #58a6ff;
        }
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card);
            padding: 3.5rem 4rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 540px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 700 4rem/1 system-ui;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--red));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2.5rem 0;
        }

        .feature {
            background: rgba(255,166,87,0.08);
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,166,87,0.2);
        }

        code {
            font: 600 1rem 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', Consolas, monospace;
            background: #21262d;
            color: var(--accent);
            padding: 0.4em 0.75em;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--link);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Trickster</h1>
        <p class="tagline"><strong>Congratulations!</strong> Your app is live.</p>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">Blazing fast routing</div>
            <div class="feature">Zero dependencies</div>
            <div class="feature">Stateless sessions</div>
            <div class="feature">Built for 2025+</div>
        </div>

        <p>Next step:</p>
        <p><code>trickster generate controller Home</code></p>

        <footer>
            Powered by <strong>Trickster</strong> •
            <a href="https://github.com/tricksterperl/trickster" target="_blank">github.com/tricksterperl/trickster</a>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>